    "shortDescription": "<p>A creature targeted by this spell is held immobile by glowing golden chains composed of pure light. The creature is paralyzed and held in place, but may attempt a new saving throw each round to end the effect. While held by the golden chains, a creature cannot use any sort of extradimensional travel, such as <i>astral projection</i>, <i>blink</i>, <i>dimension door</i>, <i>ethereal jaunt</i>, <i>etherealness</i>, <i>gate</i>, <i>maze</i>, <i>plane shift</i>, <i>shadow walk</i>, <i>teleport</i>, and similar spells and spell-like abilities. The spell does not affect creatures that are already in ethereal or astral form when the spell is cast.</p>",
